{"tid":2224090,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大媽街頭演唱與男途人跳舞 違限聚令受審罪成罰4,500元","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T09:50:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02c59720a8b5f342364939c9ecf25fb20f360373","tid":2224090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"大媽今年4月無視限聚令，與女伴在中環碼頭附近唱歌表演，更帶備膠凳放置於現場，三名男途人駐足觀看。大媽及後被警員票控組織受禁群組聚集，案件經審訊後，暫委裁判官何慧嫻今裁決指，被告自辯供詞自相矛盾，既不可信亦不可靠，相信事件正如截查被告的女警所述，被告等五人沒有維持1.5米距離，持續15分鐘，而被告亦有安排及準備涉案聚會，裁定罪名成立，罰款4,500元，准她一個月內繳交。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/6IIR54H3TVGLTEKAHLRSRCQBSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2F6IIR54H3TVGLTEKAHLRSRCQBSY%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ca41884b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2F6IIR54H3TVGLTEKAHLRSRCQBSY%2F&h=17fd3c31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/6IIR54H3TVGLTEKAHLRSRCQBSY/</a>"},{"pid":"c09c11d09599291773b801cc33ea0f85e6cc09af","tid":2224090,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6547bcdb2419410338cc53b7510da6376689c7","tid":2224090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c09c11d09599291773b801cc33ea0f85e6cc09af","tid":2224090,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse